Floodlight Load Balancer fix:

To use the fix for the Floodlight Load Balancer module, first clone Floodlight and replace two files:

1. Clone Floodlight:
        git clone https://github.com/jmiserez/floodlight.git
        git checkout hb

3. Rename folder:
        mv floodlight floodlight_fixed
        
2. Replace the following files with the two files in this folder:
        src/main/java/net/floodlightcontroller/core/internal/OFChannelHandler.java
        src/main/java/net/floodlightcontroller/loadbalancer/LoadBalancer.java

3. Compile Floodlight
        ant

